overview: EvPal is your Electric Vehicle Portal. It is the simplest and easiest way to find information about EV on the Web or Grid. Here you can interact with people like you who are interested in EV and have expertise to share. You can learn for example how to convert your gas guzzler into an efficient less costly to operate electric vehicle. Here you can visit showrooms filled with the latest EVs, find preowned electric cars and trucks/suvs. You can also trade electric vehicles, find recharge centers location, as well as parts and services including batteries, motors, controllers etc… We can help you finance your next conversion, lease, rental orpurchase of an Electric Vehicle. So relax and let your EvPal be your guide. Get your EV Domain here: http://www.evpal.dot5hosting.com/evpal/?page_id=22
